videoSnippet.title: Crazy Supercomputer Move! | Carlsen vs Donchenko  | ECCC (2018)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Magnus Carlsen vs Alexander Donchenko
EUROPEAN CLUB CUP 2018, Greece, Porto Carras Grand Resort 
15 Oct 2018.
Colle System (D04)

1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 d5 3. e3 c5 4. Nbd2 cxd4 5. exd4 Nc6 6. Bb5 Qb6 7. c4 dxc4 8. a4 a6 9. Nxc4 Qc7 10. Bxc6+ Qxc6 11. Nce5 Qd5 12. O-O Bg4 13. Nxg4 Nxg4 14. a5 Nf6 15. Bg5 e6 16. Ne5 Be7 17. Bxf6 gxf6 18. Ng4 Rd8 19. Ra4 Qb5 20. b3 f5 21. Ne3 f4 22. Nc4 Bf6 23. Nb6 Qf5 24. d5 f3 25. g3 Be5 26. Rc4 h5 27. Re1 Rh6 28. Rh4 Bc3 29. Rf4 Qh3 30. Rxf3 Bxe1 31. Qxe1 h4 32. Qe4 hxg3 33. Qa4+ Kf8 34. Qb4+ Ke8 35. Qa4+ Kf8 36. Qb4+ Ke8

34th European Club Cup and the 23rd European Women Club Cup will be simultaneously held from 11th-19th October 2018 in Porto Carras, famous Greek seaside resort in Halkidiki.

Official page http://www.europechess.org/european-club-cup-2018-regulations/
